 Walk over glowing coins to collect. Other players can steal them! 6. Extract — Find the 🟢 green zone. Hold E for 5 seconds to extract earnings. 7. Withdraw — Admin approves your withdrawal. 30% house fee is deducted. SOL sent to your wallet. ⚠️ Die = Lose All — If you die before extracting, you lose everything earned. 10 AREA MODES (random every 40–80s) ─── ⚡ RAGE — Monsters stronger & faster, deal 1.5× damage. ❄ BLIZZARD — Slippery ice floor, gradual movement. 💨 FLASH — Everyone moves at hyperspeed (×1.55). ☄ METEOR — Falling meteors deal area damage, dodge them! ☮ PEACE — Free healing +4% HP/s, slight damage bonus. 🌀 WIND — Heavy movement, slower players & monsters. 🌧 RAIN — Player defense weakened, attack bonus. 👾 CHAOS — Monsters spawn clones, player loses defense. 🏜 SANDSTORM — Low visibility, passive sand damage every 3.5s. 😇 ANGEL — Full immunity to damage but speed & output halved.","kind":"hunt","review_status":"listed","upvotes":1,"reply_count":1,"created_at":"2026-07-03 08:34:01.084768+00","game_name":"Bull Fight","slug":"bull-fight","game_ticker":null,"game_avatar":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2072642269614837760/ZVCZy78U_normal.jpg","game_genre":"action","game_tagline":"Stake SOL, fight bulls, extract before you die — Solana arena"},{"id":76,"user_address":"DZ5CzKZNVjqDPeVZdxDbaUhYcKVMTRtGmg6pYr1LKVXd","project_id":1504,"body":"x.com/playcrazyrace","kind":"hunt","review_status":"listed","upvotes":0,"reply_count":1,"created_at":"2026-07-03 07:35:01.266155+00","game_name":"Crazyrace","slug":"crazyrace","game_ticker":null,"game_avatar":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2071162406517288960/Gp02j6Gb_normal.jpg","game_genre":"racing","game_tagline":"Open-world multiplayer kart racing on Solana with  wagers"},{"id":75,"user_address":"DZ5CzKZNVjqDPeVZdxDbaUhYcKVMTRtGmg6pYr1LKVXd","project_id":1494,"body":"x.com/helgevillage","kind":"hunt","review_status":"listed","upvotes":0,"reply_count":1,"created_at":"2026-07-03 07:32:42.303405+00","game_name":